  <li>use a <a href="http://meyerweb.com/eric/tools/dencoder/">URL Decoder/Encoder</a> to turn your message into a encoded URL which you will use in step 3 (it‚Äôs easy, just click a button)</li>
  <li>use Twitter‚Äôs <a href="https://dev.twitter.com/web/tweet-button">developers</a> URL <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Hello%20world">https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Hello%20world</a> and replace ‚ÄúHello%20world‚Äù with the encoded URL from step 2 ‚Ä¶ DONE!</li>
</ol>

